high.mackenzie.autumn.lang.compiler.utils

Class MemberToHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • high.mackenzie.autumn.lang.compiler.utils.MemberToHandler

  • public final class MemberToHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    An instance of this class is used to map a setter, getter, or method to a handler function.
